PindouVerse VS Code Extension — Licensing
=========================================

This extension is part of the PindouVerse project. It is licensed under
the same terms as the parent project — the source code is licensed under
the **PolyForm Noncommercial License 1.0.0**, with a clarification that
selling physical bead artwork you produced using the software is NOT
Commercial Use.

For the full license text and clarifications, see the repository root:
- https://github.com/cangelzz/pindouverse/blob/main/LICENSE (overview + clarifications)
- https://github.com/cangelzz/pindouverse/blob/main/LICENSE-CODE (PolyForm NC 1.0.0 full text)

Earlier Releases
----------------

Extension versions through 0.8.9 inclusive were published under the MIT
license. That grant is irrevocable for those versions. This non-commercial
license applies to versions published from 0.8.10 onward.

Commercial Licensing
--------------------

For commercial licensing, open a GitHub issue at
https://github.com/cangelzz/pindouverse/issues with the label
`commercial-license` describing your intended use.

